description: Kakel Max AB is a holding company, which engages in owning and managing of shares. The firm provides assortment, services and consulting for professionals. Kakel Max AB (publ) is the parent company of Kakel & Design i Sverige AB, a Sweden-based company engaged in the provision of glazed tile, clinkers, furniture made of wood and durable materials, taps made of metals and plastics, washbasins made of ceramics, towel hangers, shower walls made of plastics, bathtubs made of ceramics, ceramic toilet bowls, plastic and metal floor drains and stone and composite countertops. The firm is primarily active in Sweden, and has its stores located in Uppsala, Gavla, Sollentuna and Arsta.
